550
00:37:09,160 --> 00:37:10,880
I'm no longer a nobody?

551
00:37:11,880 --> 00:37:14,400
I've even been in several dramas with you?

552
00:37:14,880 --> 00:37:15,800
Yes.

553
00:37:16,160 --> 00:37:18,200
And I'm now retired from showbiz.

554
00:37:18,440 --> 00:37:19,480
Retired?

555
00:37:23,720 --> 00:37:26,200
Linlin, there's something very important
you have to know.

556
00:37:26,360 --> 00:37:28,040
He is your husband

557
00:37:28,280 --> 00:37:29,400
with legal certification.

558
00:37:29,800 --> 00:37:30,920
Husband?

559
00:37:31,880 --> 00:37:35,720
Feifei, are you writing a new script
and pranking me?

560
00:37:36,080 --> 00:37:37,920
Or are we on a show?

561
00:37:38,080 --> 00:37:39,200
<i>X-Change</i>?

562
00:37:39,520 --> 00:37:43,000
Is there a hidden camera in the room?

563
00:37:43,080 --> 00:37:44,320
Mumu, they are telling the truth.

564
00:37:44,400 --> 00:37:45,600
We're really married.

565
00:37:45,680 --> 00:37:47,240
Look. This is our marriage certificate.

566
00:37:47,320 --> 00:37:48,480
MARRIAGE CERTIFICATE

567
00:37:48,560 --> 00:37:49,800
Does this trigger your memory?

568
00:37:53,080 --> 00:37:54,120
Chu Yan?

569
00:37:55,120 --> 00:37:56,440
Am I dreaming?

570
00:37:57,040 --> 00:37:58,040
Pinch me.

571
00:37:59,960 --> 00:38:01,400
See for yourself.

572
00:38:01,760 --> 00:38:03,720
This really is your marriage certificate.

573
00:38:04,120 --> 00:38:06,440
Now do you understand
that you're not dreaming

574
00:38:06,520 --> 00:38:08,040
and we're not filming?

575
00:38:10,160 --> 00:38:13,320
Have I been asleep for two years?

576
00:38:17,200 --> 00:38:18,320
Don't worry, Mumu.

577
00:38:19,000 --> 00:38:20,160
I will take good care of you.

578
00:38:20,240 --> 00:38:21,800
I'll make sure you remember.

579
00:38:23,360 --> 00:38:24,480
Sir?

580
00:38:25,120 --> 00:38:26,240
I'm sorry.

581
00:38:26,840 --> 00:38:28,880
I really don't know who you are

582
00:38:29,320 --> 00:38:31,840
and I don't know why we got married.

583
00:38:32,640 --> 00:38:34,560
I'm still so young.

584
00:38:34,760 --> 00:38:36,600
Why would I get married so early?

585
00:38:38,440 --> 00:38:40,960
The best-laid plans are no match for love.

586
00:38:41,040 --> 00:38:42,240
Don't interrupt.

587
00:38:42,840 --> 00:38:45,680
And even if we are married,

588
00:38:46,120 --> 00:38:49,000
I don't know how well we got along
after being married.

589
00:38:49,600 --> 00:38:52,360
So, I just can't accept

590
00:38:52,600 --> 00:38:54,320
the fact that you're my husband.

591
00:38:55,720 --> 00:38:56,880
Right, Chu Yan?

592
00:39:08,000 --> 00:39:10,360
Yizhou, don't worry.

593
00:39:11,000 --> 00:39:13,240
Fu Weining has been apprehended
for homicide.

594
00:39:18,760 --> 00:39:19,920
Don't dwell on it.

595
00:39:20,200 --> 00:39:21,400
She just woke up.

596
00:39:21,600 --> 00:39:22,840
She'll remember soon.

597
00:39:28,000 --> 00:39:28,880
All right.

598
00:39:29,440 --> 00:39:30,600
I should go.

599
00:39:30,680 --> 00:39:31,960
Call me if anything changes.

600
00:39:34,160 --> 00:39:35,240
Everything will be fine.

601
00:40:30,360 --> 00:40:31,400
What a coincidence.

602
00:40:32,040 --> 00:40:33,000
Yes.

603
00:40:49,840 --> 00:40:50,840
Don't be scared.

604
00:40:54,800 --> 00:40:56,360
Hello, is anyone there?

605
00:40:56,440 --> 00:40:57,680
We're stuck in the elevator.

606
00:40:58,200 --> 00:40:59,600
<i>We've sent for a maintenance crew.</i>

607
00:40:59,800 --> 00:41:01,120
<i>Please wait patiently.</i>

608
00:41:01,200 --> 00:41:02,200
Okay.

609
00:41:04,400 --> 00:41:07,320
Don't worry. Someone should be here soon.

610
00:41:08,880 --> 00:41:10,000
All right.

611
00:41:37,080 --> 00:41:38,440
You didn't bring your inhaler?

612
00:41:43,280 --> 00:41:44,920
Here, use this.

613
00:41:53,720 --> 00:41:54,920
Do you feel better?

614
00:41:58,560 --> 00:41:59,680
Thank goodness.

615
00:42:01,920 --> 00:42:02,960
By the way,

616
00:42:03,280 --> 00:42:04,440
you told me last time

617
00:42:04,880 --> 00:42:06,000
that someone in your family

618
00:42:06,560 --> 00:42:07,680
also has asthma?

619
00:42:10,160 --> 00:42:11,280
To tell you the truth,

620
00:42:11,720 --> 00:42:13,480
nobody in my family has asthma.

621
00:42:13,960 --> 00:42:14,920
Because you have it,

622
00:42:15,280 --> 00:42:17,760
I began carrying an inhaler with me

623
00:42:18,400 --> 00:42:19,960
in case you needed it one day.

624
00:42:29,160 --> 00:42:32,160
Did you come to the hospital
to see a doctor or...

625
00:42:32,960 --> 00:42:34,240
I wasn't stalking you!

626
00:42:34,840 --> 00:42:35,920
I really wasn't.

627
00:42:37,480 --> 00:42:39,280
Don't be so nervous.

628
00:42:39,680 --> 00:42:41,080
That's not what I was thinking.

629
00:42:52,280 --> 00:42:55,520
You said I was special.

630
00:42:56,360 --> 00:42:57,440
Why is that?

631
00:43:03,200 --> 00:43:05,200
Chu Yan, do you know?

632
00:43:05,480 --> 00:43:06,520
In the past,

633
00:43:06,800 --> 00:43:09,840
I never imagined that I would
ever interact with a man so naturally.

634
00:43:10,760 --> 00:43:11,760
I...

635
00:43:13,040 --> 00:43:15,000
I was kidnapped when I was a child.

636
00:43:15,360 --> 00:43:16,680
I was rescued,

637
00:43:17,120 --> 00:43:20,320
but I later grew to be afraid of men.

638
00:43:22,080 --> 00:43:24,600
I'm really scared of being with men.

639
00:43:24,920 --> 00:43:27,640
I sometimes even have an allergic reaction
if there's physical contact.

640
00:43:28,240 --> 00:43:29,920
It sounds fake,

641
00:43:30,480 --> 00:43:31,760
but it's true.

642
00:43:32,600 --> 00:43:34,000
At the cafÃ© that day,

643
00:43:34,320 --> 00:43:36,360
I discovered that
I didn't have a reaction to you.

644
00:43:37,760 --> 00:43:39,400
<i>I was so happy that day.</i>

645
00:43:39,560 --> 00:43:42,520
<i>That was the first time
I had genuine interaction with a man.</i>

646
00:43:47,880 --> 00:43:49,040
So that's why

647
00:43:49,400 --> 00:43:51,440
you used to always wear gloves.

648
00:43:52,200 --> 00:43:55,640
I came to the hospital today
for my regular psychological therapy.

649
00:43:56,920 --> 00:43:58,960
My condition has improved a lot.

650
00:44:01,120 --> 00:44:03,920
And that night...

651
00:44:04,800 --> 00:44:06,240
<i>Can the people inside hear me?</i>

652
00:44:07,480 --> 00:44:08,360
We're here.

653
00:44:08,800 --> 00:44:10,400
<i>Hold on. We're working on the problem.</i>

654
00:44:10,520 --> 00:44:11,440
<i>We'll be done soon.</i>

655
00:44:12,920 --> 00:44:13,840
Okay.

656
00:44:17,440 --> 00:44:18,440
Sorry.

657
00:44:22,360 --> 00:44:23,480
Why are you apologizing?

658
00:44:27,480 --> 00:44:29,320
Did I startle you the other day?

659
00:44:30,080 --> 00:44:31,720
I like you a lot.

660
00:44:34,440 --> 00:44:36,680
But I shouldn't have been so impolite.

661
00:45:02,360 --> 00:45:03,480
The door is open.

662
00:45:07,400 --> 00:45:08,400
Okay.

663
00:45:55,160 --> 00:45:56,200
What's wrong, Feifei?

664
00:45:56,320 --> 00:45:57,320
Writer's block?

665
00:46:02,200 --> 00:46:03,640
I'm just thinking

666
00:46:04,080 --> 00:46:06,760
that Linlin must be panicking right now.

667
00:46:07,840 --> 00:46:09,360
Everybody and everything around her

668
00:46:10,280 --> 00:46:11,720
has changed.

669
00:46:12,360 --> 00:46:13,520
She is the only one

670
00:46:14,320 --> 00:46:16,120
still living two years in the past.

671
00:46:19,360 --> 00:46:21,120
Her memory loss is temporary.

672
00:46:21,520 --> 00:46:22,840
She will recover.

673
00:46:28,360 --> 00:46:29,320
Wen Li?

674
00:46:31,800 --> 00:46:33,840
If I were to forget you,

675
00:46:34,840 --> 00:46:35,880
would you...

676
00:46:43,160 --> 00:46:44,320
I would wait for you.

677
00:46:44,720 --> 00:46:45,760
Forever.

678
00:47:47,960 --> 00:47:50,520
It doesn't seem safe
for you to live by yourself.

679
00:47:50,840 --> 00:47:52,480
Maybe you should stay with Mr. Ling.

680
00:47:52,560 --> 00:47:53,880
What's the problem?

681
00:47:54,120 --> 00:47:56,120
I lost my memory. I'm not handicapped.

682
00:47:59,400 --> 00:48:00,760
This is your apartment.

683
00:48:07,160 --> 00:48:09,240
How do you know my passcode?

684
00:48:10,040 --> 00:48:11,880
The passcode is the date
you won your first award.

685
00:48:12,560 --> 00:48:14,200
It's 180716.

686
00:48:15,520 --> 00:48:17,760
Mr. Ling, thank you for giving me a ride.

687
00:48:17,920 --> 00:48:19,440
You should head home too.

688
00:48:19,760 --> 00:48:20,720
Goodbye.

689
00:48:21,960 --> 00:48:23,040
Come in.

690
00:48:26,960 --> 00:48:27,920
Mumu.

691
00:48:28,640 --> 00:48:29,720
Is there anything else?

692
00:48:31,000 --> 00:48:32,200
This is also my home.

693
00:48:36,160 --> 00:48:38,920
Mr. Ling, since you're my husband,

694
00:48:39,200 --> 00:48:41,560
can you indulge me for a while?

695
00:48:42,160 --> 00:48:44,280
I need some time

696
00:48:44,360 --> 00:48:46,400
to process the fact that we're married.

697
00:48:46,840 --> 00:48:48,360
If you're here,

698
00:48:48,720 --> 00:48:50,680
I don't think I'll be at ease.

699
00:48:55,840 --> 00:48:57,920
Mr. Ling, you should go for now.

700
00:48:58,040 --> 00:48:59,160
Mumu is right.

701
00:48:59,320 --> 00:49:01,360
You need to give her time
to process all this.

702
00:49:04,600 --> 00:49:05,560
Okay.

703
00:49:07,200 --> 00:49:09,040
Call me immediately if you need anything.

704
00:49:09,360 --> 00:49:11,320
Sure. Get some rest.

705
00:49:11,440 --> 00:49:12,280
Bye.

706
00:49:42,280 --> 00:49:43,320
Wen Li?

707
00:49:45,000 --> 00:49:46,560
How are you spending
Chinese Valentine's Day?

708
00:49:46,880 --> 00:49:48,400
Chinese Valentine's Day?

709
00:49:48,880 --> 00:49:52,480
I prepared
a romantic candlelight dinner for Feifei.

710
00:49:52,560 --> 00:49:54,360
Wine and candles.

711
00:49:54,720 --> 00:49:56,960
I hear women like the romantic ambiance.

712
00:49:58,000 --> 00:49:59,040
Are you sure?

713
00:50:00,880 --> 00:50:02,000
Yes.

714
00:50:02,960 --> 00:50:04,440
Candlelight dinner?

715
00:50:05,600 --> 00:50:06,720
That's so corny!

716
00:50:06,800 --> 00:50:08,040
What age is this?

717
00:50:08,160 --> 00:50:10,440
Do you think women would like
such an old-fashioned idea?

718
00:50:10,520 --> 00:50:12,880
I'm telling you,
if you prepare that for Feifei,

719
00:50:13,320 --> 00:50:14,840
your relationship will go downhill.

720
00:50:15,960 --> 00:50:17,000
No way!

721
00:50:17,080 --> 00:50:19,280
You bet! Giving her money
would be better than this.

722
00:50:19,480 --> 00:50:20,960
I suggest you come up with something else.

723
00:50:22,920 --> 00:50:24,800
Boss, I have to make a call
to cancel reservations.

724
00:50:24,880 --> 00:50:26,040
Come up with a new idea.

725
00:50:33,560 --> 00:50:35,760
Candlelight dinner.

726
00:52:08,480 --> 00:52:12,240
Did Ling Yizhou send Ms. Huang
to spy on me?

727
00:52:15,880 --> 00:52:17,280
Where are the marriage certificates?

728
00:52:21,680 --> 00:52:22,800
MARRIAGE CERTIFICATE

729
